#: ../../en/data-memory.rst:2
msgid "Case Data and Memory"
msgstr "案例数据与长期记忆"

#: ../../en/data-memory.rst:5
msgid "Case File Shape"
msgstr "案例文件结构"

#: ../../en/data-memory.rst:7
msgid "AnnaAgent case files are JSON or YAML documents containing a seeker profile, case report, and previous-session dialogue history."
msgstr "AnnaAgent 案例文件可以是 JSON 或 YAML，包含来访者画像、案例报告和历史疗程对话。"

#: ../../en/data-memory.rst:10
msgid "Required high-level fields:"
msgstr "主要字段："

#: ../../en/data-memory.rst:12
msgid "``id``"
msgstr "``id``"

#: ../../en/data-memory.rst:13
msgid "Stable case identifier."
msgstr "稳定案例 ID。"

#: ../../en/data-memory.rst:15
msgid "``seeker_id``"
msgstr "``seeker_id``"

#: ../../en/data-memory.rst:16
msgid "Stable seeker identifier used for memory filtering."
msgstr "稳定来访者 ID，用于长期记忆过滤。"

#: ../../en/data-memory.rst:18
msgid "``portrait``"
msgstr "``portrait``"

#: ../../en/data-memory.rst:19
msgid "Demographic attributes, risk scores, symptoms, and optional metadata."
msgstr "人口学信息、风险分数、症状和可选元数据。"

#: ../../en/data-memory.rst:21
msgid "``report``"
msgstr "``report``"

#: ../../en/data-memory.rst:22
msgid "Structured counseling case report. The public sample uses Chinese report keys."
msgstr "结构化咨询案例报告。公开样例使用中文字段。"

#: ../../en/data-memory.rst:24
msgid "``conversation`` or ``previous_conversations``"
msgstr "``conversation`` 或 ``previous_conversations``"

#: ../../en/data-memory.rst:25
msgid "Previous-session turns. Each turn should include ``role`` and ``content``."
msgstr "历史疗程对话，每轮至少包含 ``role`` 和 ``content``。"

#: ../../en/data-memory.rst:27
msgid "Validate a file before running experiments:"
msgstr "运行实验前先校验："

#: ../../en/data-memory.rst:35
msgid "Create a Sample"
msgstr "生成样例"

#: ../../en/data-memory.rst:41
msgid "Use the generated sample as a format reference, then replace the fictional content with your own ethically permitted data."
msgstr "可以把生成文件当作格式参考，然后替换为你有伦理许可的数据。"

#: ../../en/data-memory.rst:45
msgid "Long-Term Memory"
msgstr "长期记忆"

#: ../../en/data-memory.rst:47
msgid "AnnaAgent uses LanceDB for local long-term memory. Previous conversations and reports are chunked into memory records such as:"
msgstr "AnnaAgent 使用 LanceDB 存储本地长期记忆。历史对话和报告会切分为多种 memory record："

#: ../../en/data-memory.rst:50
msgid "``conversation_turn``"
msgstr "``conversation_turn``"

#: ../../en/data-memory.rst:51
msgid "``conversation_window``"
msgstr "``conversation_window``"

#: ../../en/data-memory.rst:52
msgid "``session_summary``"
msgstr "``session_summary``"

#: ../../en/data-memory.rst:53
msgid "``report_section``"
msgstr "``report_section``"

#: ../../en/data-memory.rst:54
msgid "``report_summary``"
msgstr "``report_summary``"

#: ../../en/data-memory.rst:56
msgid "Index a case:"
msgstr "索引案例："

#: ../../en/data-memory.rst:62
msgid "Search memory:"
msgstr "检索记忆："

#: ../../en/data-memory.rst:68
msgid "Inspect or reset memory:"
msgstr "查看或重置记忆："

#: ../../en/data-memory.rst:77
msgid "Reusable Prompt State"
msgstr "可复用 Prompt State"

#: ../../en/data-memory.rst:79
msgid "``full`` states run the complete dynamic initialization pipeline. They include the generated complaint chain, status summary, sampled situation, style analysis, and the final seeker system prompt. Save this state when you want to reuse the initialized seeker later with ``anna chat --state`` or the service API."
msgstr "``full`` state 会运行完整动态初始化流水线，包含生成的主诉链、状态摘要、采样情境、说话风格分析和最终 seeker system prompt。需要稍后通过 ``anna chat --state`` 或 service API 复用已初始化 seeker 时，请保存这个 state。"

#: ../../en/data-memory.rst:86
msgid "AnnaAgent does not support a shortcut that builds a prompt directly from a raw case without running initialization, because that bypasses the seeker simulation modules and produces the wrong prompt format."
msgstr "AnnaAgent 不支持绕过初始化、直接从原始 case 拼 prompt 的快捷方式，因为这会跳过 seeker simulation modules，并生成错误的 prompt 格式。"
